<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Welcome to ActiveRabbit <%= @new_plan.to_s.titleize %></title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    h2 { margin: 24px 0 12px; font-size: 16px; }
    p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #333; font-size: 14px; }

    .success-box {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .success-box p { color: #166534; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }

    .plan-box {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: block;
      margin: 12px 0 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .feature-grid li {
      padding: 6px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .feature-grid li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .feature-grid li strong { color: #111; }

    .check {
      color: #16a34a;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 6px;
    }

    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0 8px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #667eea;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .tips {
      background: #eff6ff;
      border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .tips p { color: #1e40af; margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 14px; }
    .tips ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    .tips li { font-size: 13px; color: #1e3a5f; padding: 3px 0; }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;">
          <%= image_tag "faviicons/favicon-512.png",
            width: 48,
            height: 48,
            style: "display:block;margin-right:16px;" %>

          <div style="text-align:left;">
            <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;">
              Welcome to <%= @new_plan.to_s.titleize %> Plan
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;opacity:0.9;margin-top:2px;">
              ActiveRabbit — AI-Powered Error Tracking for Rails
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="success-box">
        <p><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong>You're all set!</strong> Your ActiveRabbit account
        <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> has been upgraded to the
        <strong><%= @new_plan.to_s.titleize %></strong> plan. Your usage counters have been reset — you're starting fresh.</p>
      </div>

      <% plan_key = @new_plan.to_s.downcase.to_sym %>
      <% quotas = ResourceQuotas::PLAN_QUOTAS[plan_key] || ResourceQuotas::PLAN_QUOTAS[:team] %>

      <div class="plan-box">
        <strong>Your <%= @new_plan.to_s.titleize %> plan includes:</strong>
        <ul class="feature-grid">
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(quotas[:events]) %></strong> errors per month</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:ai_summaries] %></strong> AI error summaries per month</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:pull_requests] %></strong> pull requests per month</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:projects] %></strong> projects</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:data_retention_days] %></strong> days data retention</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:uptime_monitors] %></strong> uptime monitors</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> <strong><%= quotas[:status_pages] %></strong> status pages</li>
          <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Email &amp; Slack notifications</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tips">
        <p><strong>Get the most out of your plan:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use <strong>AI Analysis</strong> on any error to get root cause analysis and fix suggestions</li>
          <li>Connect <strong>Slack</strong> to get instant error alerts in your team channel</li>
          <li>Set up <strong>Uptime Monitors</strong> to know when your app goes down</li>
          <li>Generate <strong>Pull Requests</strong> directly from AI-suggested fixes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="<%= dashboard_url(host: ENV.fetch('APP_HOST', 'localhost:3000'), protocol: Rails.env.production? ? 'https' : 'http') %>" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #777; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 20px;">
        Questions? Reply to this email — we're happy to help you get set up.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      ActiveRabbit – AI-Powered Error Tracking for Rails
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
